http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Tribune\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The National Tribune\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Tribune\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Tribune\"}, {\"begin\": 5498, \"end\": 5507, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.841839209393565e-14, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We endeavor to give the Australian community greater transparency and access to government information and other developments free from encroaching corporate, ideological or any other interests/influences.More  We acknowledge the Traditional Custodians of Country throughout Australia and their continuing connection to land, culture and community.\", \"from\": 5578, \"to\": 5926, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5602, \"end\": 5612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999469067786377, \"rank\": 5.251824253179431e-05, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 5853, \"end\": 5862, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.841839209393565e-14, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00c2\\u00a9 2025 -The National Tribune Australia\", \"from\": 5928, \"to\": 5967, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5937, \"end\": 5957, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Tribune\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The National Tribune\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Tribune\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Tribune\"}, {\"be